# Pashudhan AI App Testing Checklist

- [ ] Open http://localhost:5173/
- [ ] Wait 2 seconds for the dashboard to load
- [ ] Click the "Health" tab in the bottom navigation
- [ ] Wait 1 second
- [ ] Click the "Scan" tab
- [ ] Click the "Scan AI" button to simulate a scan and wait 3 seconds
- [ ] Click the "Milk" tab
- [ ] Click the "Helper" tab
- [ ] Type "Hello" in the chat and click send
- [ ] Verify all tabs and functionalities
